platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A rare kind of triumph, Prune takes a simple idea—pruning trees—and shapes it into a creative, deeply playable puzzle game. The visuals echo the style of Japanese painting in striking fashion, and the beautiful music instills a contemplative tone as you swipe to trim the limbs of a rapidly growing tree and guide it around obstacles. There’s no frantic pace, no demanding skills to master—only a quietly bewitching and unforgettable experience.

A rare kind of triumph, Prune takes a simple idea—pruning trees—and shapes it into a creative, deeply playable puzzle game. The visuals echo the style of Japanese painting in striking fashion, and the beautiful music instills a contemplative tone as you swipe to trim the limbs of a rapidly growing tree and guide it around obstacles. There’s no frantic pace, no demanding skills to master—only a quietly bewitching and unforgettable experience.

Avec Prune, découvrez un monde de sérénité où la culture et l’entretien de vos arbres est un art. Chaque niveau demande un tact infini, à la recherche des moindres rayons de soleil et au défi des terres les plus inhospitalières. Portez toute votre attention sur vos créations sur arbre pour transformer vos parties en une expérience de jeu unique.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: A contemplative and creative experience - trimming trees has never been so beautiful.
